// first_system_boss — capstone of the intro-v1 vertical slice.
//
// Built out by intro-v1 Task 07. Replaces the Task 06 stub with a
// small two-phase boss arena, a P5 Route Memory reward, and a
// return-shortcut LoadingZone back to Drain Market so the intro
// becomes a gridvania knot rather than a one-way corridor.
//
// Width 1280 / height 768 — same row as combat_calibration_lab.
//
// Transitions:
// - Left-edge EdgeExit `boss_from_combat_lab` ← combat_calibration_lab/combat_lab_to_boss
// - Right-edge Door `boss_return_to_drain` → drain_alley/drain_from_boss_return
//   Door activation so the return shortcut is something the player
//   *chooses*, not an accidental teleport when they wander to the
//   right wall. drain_alley side wired in the same change.
//
// Boss: BossSpawn with `brain: PhaseScript:clockwork_warden`. The
// clockwork_warden profile is the existing audit-engine boss in the
// project (formerly gradient_sentinel); it already has registered
// behavior, sprites, and quest hooks, so wiring the intro-v1 boss
// slot to it costs nothing while giving the playtest a real boss
// fight rather than a placeholder.
//
// P5 reward: PickupSpawn drops a `flag:intro_p5_route_memory_received`
// story flag the player can pick up after the encounter ends.
// Task 08 will gate it behind boss death; for the intro-v1 minimum
// the pickup sits on a high ledge that is only reachable post-fight
// (the boss occupies the path during the fight).
//
// Layout (1280×768):
//
//   +--------------------------------------------------------+
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ ceiling ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ |
//   |                                                        |
//   |  ▒▒▒[upper read]▒▒▒▒                ▒▒▒[upper read]▒▒  |
//   |                                                        |
//   |             ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒[P5 pickup]▒▒▒▒▒▒▒                  |
//   |                                                        |
//   |       ▒▒▒[drop-through]▒▒        ▒▒[drop-through]▒▒    |
//   |                                                        |
//   |   ←entry                                       return→ |
//   |                       [BOSS]                           |
//   |▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ floor ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒ |
//   +--------------------------------------------------------+

